metadata.name: Bubble Planets #1
metadata.description:
Each planet is unique and has its own special character. A smile and a positive vibe is the hallmark of each planet. Bubbles the universe in which the planets live has unique properties, thanks to which each of them evolves and develops. The planets live in harmony and abundance, they are friends with each other and are ready to come to the aid of those in need.

Bubble Planets donates royalties to save the planet.
